Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要生活在地下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像地上不能生存
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來到底發生了什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像發生了什麼不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是被什麼奇怪的東西襲擊了什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所大家就都搬到地下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全聽不懂啊 這個說明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 我們的未來竟然變成了這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說並不是只有這個未來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說我們的未來不是只有一個 而是有很多個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 未來就是未來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難說明 但是時空這東西隨著時間的改變有無數個存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說這裏只是可能性之一的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能性之一的未來?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛? 為什麼愛會...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個世界的愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次還帶著男生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗麗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小美保
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是麗麗 美保是媽媽的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的是個笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 你難道不知道龍騎兵都在找你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我雖然知道 但是因為被帶到這裏來了...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 幹什麼說的像別人的事一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~再這樣下去又要被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~那又要被塞到水槽裏面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 去阿姨那裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 為什麼會到這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 你是佑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人懷念啊 還只有12歲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是愛嗎 難道不覺得她太親切了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 到裏面來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被龍騎兵發現了就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 感覺好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被聽到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉 到正下方來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊OK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量不足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎~騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鷺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充電電池
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅秧給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鷺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把兩人都帶回來 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被逆算固定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實鳶也這麼說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是難懂的話?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 如果不考慮下讓你們回去的方法...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在由我來保護遙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和那傢伙約定過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保護遙啊 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的話一定要去那個房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來時的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉移裝置的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼趕快...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿來喝的東西了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒...沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使...使不出力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 振作一點 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大哥哥的身體...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 我要在這裏 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥 呼吸都沒有了...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 有微小點侵入拉庫利瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鳶 鳶回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼不讓我進去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑..佑會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:09:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 你是一個堅強的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 你聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在發生了量子革命的我們的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的物體都進入了量子狀態之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時空整體就是一個無法確定的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們人類自身也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們...是沒有觀測者的不安定的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀測者?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我們把一切都粒子技術化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並存入量子電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此讓這個世界安定化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並把這個世界命名為拉庫利瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說 沒有資料技術化的人類 是不能存在在這裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以佑他...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不是好好的在這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前來的時候就已經被記錄下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 從這裏開始是重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實佑看上去像死了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要那個存在是不安定的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的死也是曖昧的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是說佑現在處於死的時空和生的時空重迭的狀態下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了的佑和活著的佑?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著的佑也在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 所以你不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩的你擁有把看到的東西固定化的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在的你看到了死的狀態的佑的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑的死就會成為確實的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:11:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能看到活著的狀態的佑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並意識到互相的存在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑的活著的狀態就會被確定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼活著的佑在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是...哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是天堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你會到這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我已經不能讀透時空的意識了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑在香格里拉?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想救他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就和我一起去香格里拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅秧 你背叛了拉庫利瑪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被讓龍之轉矩逃走的你說教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你想要幫助殺了梟的鴉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我 愛 不是鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇和佑到最後還是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他還說想要見愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是鴉 是諾因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我討厭香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅秧 我不會把遙交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救佑 我必須去香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去的話 佑就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑他...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗麗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉庫利瑪就要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底就是那點程度的時空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時空的收縮不僅僅是香格里拉的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是整頓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要的東西的消失是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉 你也是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個時空接受了這根線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭受到了比預想還要難以忍受的痛苦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有一切只有痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時空的存在只是為了嘗受痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我在香格里拉就可以被拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有龍之轉矩 就可以讓香格里拉接受我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那個沒有痛苦 可以幸福的生活的時空去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們所嚮往的幸福的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們所嚮往的? 那大家在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有形態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個只依靠意識而存在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意識?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須去 否則佑會死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會把佑救回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾因 讓我去香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是救了我和勇的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我和你也見過一面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是藤原勇15年以後的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 那個勇被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了他的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是15年後的你殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15年後的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被鴉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 因為我就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的未來註定要殺死自己的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:18:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 那是騙人的——！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉 終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到永恆的香格里拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時空...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉把我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都追到這裏來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我看中的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話一定能成為那樣的龍騎兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是象我這樣難堪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我這幅模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望來香格里拉的結果就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑我吧 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑愚蠢的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他解體了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佑在叫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生活在無限的不幸之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後一直都是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到死為止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的時空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
